OL,6,FA Leeds food bank is spending
OL,7,Fthousands of pounds every month to
OL,8,Fkeep up with rising demand and falling
OL,9,Fdonations.
OL,11,FLeeds North and West Foodbank says it
OL,12,Fis spending over #12,000 each month to
OL,13,Fkeep up with increased demand and drop
OL,14,Fin donations, which is placing extra
OL,15,Fpressure on the service.
OL,17,FKaren Burgon, Chief Executive of the
OL,18,Ffood bank said: "We do genuinely get
OL,19,Fpeople who come who haven't eaten for
OL,20,Fa couple of days"
