OL,6,F"Often people really put off coming to
OL,7,Fus until things are so desperate that
OL,8,Fthey don't have any other options."
OL,10,FNew research from the Charities Aid
OL,11,FFoundation (CAF) highlights the issue
OL,12,Fis nationwide, with 83% of UK
OL,13,Fcharities seeing an increased demand
OL,14,Ffor their services over the last year.
OL,16,F86% of charities expect demand to
OL,17,Ffurther increase over the next year.
OL,19,FCAF are calling on the Government to
OL,20,Fintroduce policies to encourage more
OL,21,Fdonations.
