OL,6,FNeil Heslop OBE , Chief Executive of
OL,7,Fthe Charities Aid Foundation said:
OL,8,F"Whether it's a local community cafe,
OL,9,Fcutting-edge health project, or
OL,10,Finitiatives that transform the lives
OL,11,Fof homeless people, charities are
OL,12,Fcentral to our social fabric.
OL,14,F"Yet their role has never been tougher.
OL,16,F"With ever-increasing demand,
OL,17,Finflationary pressures remaining and
OL,18,Fsignificantly fewer funding
OL,19,Fopportunities, charities cannot pass
OL,20,Fon costs and are having to do much
OL,21,Fmore with less," he added.
